user.name: Happy Holidayopolis
user.bio: Holidayopolis isn’t just for visiting, it’s for experiencing. Zoom on over to our fair city at HappyHolidayopolis.com and take in a free concert, storytelling, cooking class and more in one of our fine neighborhoods ... Hanukkah Town, Christmas Village, Kwanzaa Heights, Solstice Circle, and Diwaliwood! Come celebrate your favorite holiday... or learn a little bit about someone else's favorite!
user.short_bio: Holidayopolis is committed to bringing light, love and joy to the world. We are committed to antiracism, nonviolent communication and positivity resonance.

user.name: Christ Fellowship Miami
user.bio: Christ Fellowship is a multi-generational, multi-cultural and international church meeting in multiple locations across Miami, the Caribbean, Latin America, and online. Whether you’re soaking up the tropical sun in Jamaica, hiking in Colombia, or enjoying a paska in Ukraine, we believe Miami is one of the most strategic places on the planet to share the love of Jesus with the world.
user.short_bio: Christ Fellowship is a multi-generational, multi-cultural and international church meeting in multiple locations.

user.name: Mazal Fabrikant
user.bio:
Matthias has been working for over 20 years as a freelance photographer in the fields of Editorial and Commercial photography for National as well as International clients. In the past years he started to extend photography with Computer Generated Imagery. Besides his commercial photography, he has participated in group and solo exhibitions with his artistic and travel photography. 

Since 2007 he has been teaching Photography primary in the Department Visual Communication  and as well in the Department Knowledge Visualization (from 2018) and Master Design Studies at the Zurich University of Fine Arts (ZHdK). Beside this he also has various guest lectureships, such as at the Bezalel Academy of Arts in Jerusalem (from 2019), the Lucerne University of Applied Science and Arts (from 2020) etc.

I feel specially attracted by projects that imply a multidisciplinary creative solution: real photography or CGI. Digital or tactile. Or both. I love to experiment and provide technically outstanding visual solutions, making sleek, clean and bold images. And by the way: Mazal Fabrikant means Happy Manufacturer – because it's always about getting excited and the feeling of enthusiasm.

user.name: Tierce Green
user.bio: Tierce Green is a speaker, writer and consultant. He is the Director of the Authentic Manhood Initiative which is building a global network of men reaching men with the timeless principles of biblical manhood. He led over a thousand men each week for seven years in a seasonal gathering called The Quest in The Woodlands, Texas. He is on the presentation team of 33 The Series for Authentic Manhood which has reached well over a million men around the world.
user.short_bio: Speaker, Writer and Consultant. Director of the Authentic Manhood Initiative.
